## Here is information on sending in your completed application form

Once you have completed filling in your application form you must complete these three steps:

- Submit the form;
- Gather all the requested documents and information. They are needed to establish your eligibility and to determine the amount of assistance you could get;
- Send the documents using the online services, by mail or by submitting documents in person at one of the [Services Québec offices](https://www.localisateur.servicesquebec.gouv.qc.ca/en). Once the Services Québec office receives your forms, you will have to go in person for identity verification.

